### 1. Health check (no auth required)
GET {{base}}/health

###

### 2. Login — get JWT token  ← RUN THIS FIRST, then update @token above
# @name login
POST {{base}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

###

### 3. Me — verify local JWT is accepted
GET {{base}}/me-local
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 4. Products — browse catalogue (paginated)
GET {{base}}/products?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 5. Product by ID
GET {{base}}/products/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 6. Inventory summary — stock across all products
GET {{base}}/inventory/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 7. Inventory by product ID
GET {{base}}/inventory/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 8. Suppliers list
GET {{base}}/suppliers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 9. Add supplier  ← run this before POST product (products need a valid SupplierId)
POST {{base}}/suppliers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "companyName": "Rajasthan Marble Co.",
  "contactName": "Rajesh Kumar",
  "contactPhone": "+91-9876543210",
  "contactEmail": "rajesh@rajasthanmarble.com",
  "address": "123 Marble Street, Kishangarh",
  "country": "India",
  "specialisation": "Makrana White Marble"
}

###

### 10. Add product  ← use the SupplierId returned by block 9
POST {{base}}/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Makrana White 60x60",
  "material": "Marble",
  "format": "Tile",
  "surface": "Polished",
  "color": "White",
  "size": "60x60cm",
  "countryOfOrigin": "India",
  "pricePerUnit": 48.50,
  "supplierId": 1
}

###

### 11. Adjust inventory — commit stock (requires a valid stockLotId)
### AdjustmentType: "Commit" (reserves stock for an order) or "Release" (frees it back)
POST {{base}}/inventory/adjust
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "stockLotId": 1,
  "quantity": 10,
  "type": "Commit",
  "reason": "Reserved for order ORD-001"
}

###

### 12. Adjust inventory — release stock back
POST {{base}}/inventory/adjust
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "stockLotId": 1,
  "quantity": 10,
  "type": "Release",
  "reason": "Order ORD-001 cancelled"
}
